###> symfony/framework-bundle ###
# APP_SECRET is intentionally NOT defined here.
# Load order is .env -> .env.local -> .env.dev -> .env.dev.local (later wins),
# so any value set here would OVERRIDE the uncommitted secret in .env.local.
# Keep .env.dev free of secrets; provision the dev APP_SECRET via .env.local
# (gitignored) or a real OS environment variable. See .env header warning.
###< symfony/framework-bundle ###